OL,3,CParalympian Tanni Grey-Thompson had to
OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,FBaroness Grey-Thompson, from Cardiff,
OL,8,Fwas a wheelchair racer and competed in
OL,9,Ffive Games between 1988 and 2004. She
OL,10,Fclaimed 11 gold medals, plus four
OL,11,Fsilvers and a bronze, and was created
OL,12,Fa Life Peer in 2010.
OL,14,FShe told BBC's Today programme she
OL,15,Fmissed her 7.15pm train and got on the
OL,16,F7.45pm service, but when she arrived
OL,17,Fat King's Cross no-one was there to
OL,18,Fmeet her.
