OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,F"I waited five minutes before I put
OL,8,Fanything on social media, because
OL,9,Fthat's, you're meant to leave, sort of
OL,10,Ffive minutes," she added.
OL,12,F"But after 16 minutes of sitting at
OL,13,FKing's Cross, no-one in sight, there
OL,14,Fwere a couple of cleaners, but they're
OL,15,Fnot insured or able to help me off, I
OL,16,Fdecided that I'd crawl off the train.
