OL,3,CParalympian Tanni Grey-Thompson had to
OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,F"It is now going to be 100 years
OL,8,Fbefore we have level boarding and I
OL,9,Fcan get on a train without the
OL,10,Fpermission or support of a non-
OL,11,Fdisabled person.
OL,13,F"So I'm still quite angry this
OL,14,Fmorning, I thought I was over it, but
OL,15,FI'm not, because I can still just
OL,16,Fabout get off the train if I have to.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
