OL,7,FAsked why the Disability
OL,8,FDiscrimination Act has been "kicked
OL,9,Fdown the road", she said: "Some of
OL,10,Fit's cost, some of it is when trains
OL,11,Fare being procured level boarding is
OL,12,Fnot in the contract, there are some
OL,13,Fcompanies who build trains who don't
OL,14,Freally want to build level boarding,
OL,15,Fso make them much more expensive. And
OL,16,Fit all just gets accepted and we get
OL,17,Fforgotten about.
