OL,4,C'crawl off train' at London King's
OL,5,CCross
OL,7,F"And there are some, you know,
OL,8,Fbrighter sort of sparks, Liverpool
OL,9,Fhave a closed loop, they have level
OL,10,Fboarding. Some of the Greater Anglia
OL,11,Ftrains have level boarding. But it's
OL,12,Fan old network, I accept it. It's not
OL,13,Fcheap or easy to do, but at what point
OL,14,Fis the Government, any government,
OL,15,Fgoing to step in and say, OK, we need
OL,16,Fto make a change."
OL,18,FLNER managing director David Horne
OL,19,Fwrote on X: "My sincere apologies for
OL,20,Fthis Tanni.
