OL,5,CCross
OL,7,F"Something has clearly gone wrong here
OL,8,Fand we've let you down.
OL,10,F"We'll investigate what went wrong and
OL,11,Fshare the details."
OL,13,FAn LNER spokesperson said: "We are
OL,14,Fsorry to understand there has been an
OL,15,Fissue at London King's Cross station
OL,16,Fon Monday evening.
OL,18,F"We are in the process of
OL,19,Finvestigating this and are in contact
OL,20,Fwith the customer directly."
